<p>Be sure to mark your calendars for the next global gatherings: <a href="https://asia.wordcamp.org/2026/">WordCamp Asia 2026</a>&nbsp; in Mumbai, India, <a href="https://europe.wordcamp.org/2026/">WordCamp Europe 2026</a>&nbsp; in Kraków, Poland, and WordCamp US 2026 in Phoenix, Arizona. We can’t wait to see you at the next chapter of the WordPress story.</p>



